channel.title: NEED HELP with auto restarter
channel.description: Ok so heres my problem. I have an autorestarter, great right? wrong! Everytime my server runs it opens java.exe, so....everytime the autorestarter runs it will start java.exe....without closing the first one, making multiple java.exe's eventually crash my server. Anyone know how to end the previous process?
